# Multiplayer server WebSocket endpoint — OPTIONAL.
#
# Leave it UNSET for local + same-network (LAN) play: the client auto-derives
# the server address from where the page was loaded (host's localhost / the
# host's LAN IP for guests), on the fixed port 2567.
#
# Set it only to point at a fixed/remote server, e.g. production:
#   Pages is HTTPS → MUST be wss:  wss://<your-railway-domain>
# VITE_SERVER_URL=wss://your-app.up.railway.app
